>采访时</a>解释道：“我们只是随机听到詹姆斯·墨菲的消息，这真的很有趣，因为我们不知道他是谁！他发了一封非常可爱、充满情感的电子邮件，他说，“你让我的信仰重新回到了音乐中”。然后他要求我们支持布里克斯顿学院的他们。”</p><p>您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/all-points-east-tickets/artist/5245909?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=RNAxOYVh5xyPWWl31GWJ3xHTUkH3XD09nRXHRo0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到 All Points East 2024 LCD 音响系统的剩余门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3771605" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3771605" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3771605" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LCD-Soundsystem-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节现场 LCD 音响系统，摄影：Andy Ford" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LCD-Soundsystem-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LCD-Soundsystem-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LCD-Soundsystem-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LCD-Soundsystem-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LCD-Soundsystem-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LCD-Soundsystem-Glastonbury-2024-credit-Andy-Ford-NME@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3771605" class="wp-caption-text"> LCD 音响系统在 Glastonbury 2024 现场直播。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford</figcaption></figure><p> 2024 年音乐节的主角还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/loyle-carner-confirmed-as-first-headliner-for-londons-all-points-east-2024-35